                                                                             GIT MERGE

 1> What is merge ?

= merge is the process of combining the change from one branch into another branch. 


2> why do we use merge ? 

=  #> to combine completed feature into the main branch
   #> to keep the main branch stable while development happens in seprate branches. 
   #> to safely integrate few feature after testing.
   #> to combine work from multiple developer into one project.


3> git merge [branch name] = this command is used to merge a branch.
 
   
important = always switch to the destination branch before merging.


